  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下基础设施的流量入口架构。核心组件是IngressController，但它在不同场景下有三个实例：Audit、Bail和Barg。另外还需要Redis缓存和负载均衡器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Audit、Bail、Barg都是IngressController的实例。那Redis缓存和负载均衡器怎么命名？还有Place和Press这两个节点，它们和主架构是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Code代表Redis缓存，Define是负载均衡器。Place到Press是一条独立的数据流，暂时不连到核心架构。另外还需要Signal和Risk两个节点，它们形成一条链：Risk指向Signal，Signal再指向Barg。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出基础结构：Audit、Bail、Barg三个IngressController，Code作为Redis缓存，Define作为负载均衡器。然后加上Risk→Signal→Barg的链路，以及独立的Place→Press。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Barg和Bail之间应该是双向关系，它们互相依赖。还有Define要连接到Barg，作为负载均衡器的下游。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Barg↔Bail双向连接，Define→Barg。那Audit和Code的连接关系呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Audit直接连到Define，Code也连到Define。也就是说，Redis缓存和其中一个IngressController都汇聚到负载均衡器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新：Audit→Define，Code→Define。现在检查整体连通性——Audit、Bail、Barg三个入口，Code缓存，Define负载均衡，Risk→Signal→Barg监控链，以及独立的Place→Press。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我刚才说错了。Bail不是连到Define，Bail应该直接连到Barg。让我重新理一下：Bail→Barg，然后Barg和Bail互相指向形成循环依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，修正为Bail→Barg，同时保留Barg→Bail的双向关系。那Audit还是保持连Define对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Audit→Define不变。最终架构确认：三个IngressController实例（Audit/Bail/Barg），Bail和Barg双向绑定，Audit走Define负载均衡，Code缓存也接入Define，Risk→Signal→Barg形成监控链路，Place→Press独立运行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
